dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Eugene Miller. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Pamela. How can I assist you today?
I need to file a new claim. I was involved in a car accident last week.
I'm sorry to hear that, Pamela. To better assist you, could you please provide me with the date and location of the accident?
The accident occurred on the twenty second of August in downtown Riverside.
Thank you, Pamela. One last thing before we proceed, could you also verify your policy number for me, please?
Of course, my policy number is A zero four five seven two B.
Thank you, Pamela, for providing the necessary information. I will assist you with filing the new claim. Is there anything else you would like to add before we proceed?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Pamela. Thank you for reaching out to us. Have a great day!
